27:23.093 --> 27:27.431
He was just fucking with you,
trying to see if you knew anything.

27:27.514 --> 27:31.351
Probably had box men coming in all day,
giving them the same routine.

27:32.310 --> 27:36.106
He's just shaking the trees.

27:37.065 --> 27:39.818
Keep quiet. Stick to the plan.

27:41.486 --> 27:42.487
Got it.

27:45.073 --> 27:47.367
"Steiner's furious."

27:47.451 --> 27:48.910
[laughing]

27:50.245 --> 27:51.705
Gotta piss.

28:06.720 --> 28:07.721
[unzips pants]

28:07.805 --> 28:10.014
- [urinating]
- [belches]

28:10.098 --> 28:11.433
[speaks Hindi]
Who's there?

28:13.644 --> 28:15.771
[speaks German]
Is there a woman in here?

28:16.772 --> 28:19.899
[speaks Hindi] What do you mean is there
a woman in here. This is my bathroom.

28:22.611 --> 28:25.947
[speaks German] Your bathroom? Lady,
I think you may be even drunker than I am.

28:27.157 --> 28:29.827
[speaks Hindi] I'm not drunk,
though obviously you are!

28:38.293 --> 28:40.044
[speaks German]
What are you talking about?

28:42.255 --> 28:43.965
[speaks Hindi] I know that voice--

28:48.887 --> 28:50.138
[speaks German] Where are you?

28:50.889 --> 28:54.017
[speaks Hindi]
You are the singing man in my dream.

28:54.100 --> 28:55.769
[speaks Hindi] I can't see you.

28:58.146 --> 28:59.314
[Felix] Wolfgang?

29:01.274 --> 29:02.984
What the hell language is that?

29:06.321 --> 29:08.198
[knocking at door]

29:08.281 --> 29:13.036
[woman] Kala? Are you all right?
I heard you talking to someone.

29:14.162 --> 29:18.750
Oh, just... to myself.

29:19.417 --> 29:20.544
Oh.

29:20.627 --> 29:24.464
Well, if you ever need someone
to talk to about things...

29:24.548 --> 29:25.965
Things?

29:26.049 --> 29:29.887
Things that happen
on a girl's wedding night.

29:29.969 --> 29:31.971
Auntie, it's OK.

29:33.807 --> 29:35.767
We have the Internet.

29:35.851 --> 29:37.268
Oh!

29:37.352 --> 29:39.270
I knew that thing
was good for something.

29:39.354 --> 29:40.898
Mm.

29:45.736 --> 29:48.112
[Lito]
Am I making my mind up as it happens?

29:48.947 --> 29:51.909
- Or do I already know?
- You tell me, baby. You're the guy.

29:51.991 --> 29:54.870
Just make it real.
I want your guts on this one, yes?

29:54.953 --> 29:57.080
I think I should have a line
before I reach Don Carlos.

29:57.163 --> 29:59.624
- Sure. Whatever. Put it in. Yes.
- OK.

29:59.708 --> 30:01.668
So we're gonna rehearse
with the squibs, right?

30:01.752 --> 30:04.713
Fuck, no! I want chaos, confusion.

30:04.796 --> 30:07.465
I want blanks firing, squibs exploding.

30:07.549 --> 30:11.428
Total mayhem surrounding the meaningless
destruction of precious art.

30:11.511 --> 30:14.347
That's-- That's the message of this film.

30:14.431 --> 30:17.935
And without the grit of reality,
nobody's going to believe it.

30:18.017 --> 30:19.853
- OK? Your guts?
- OK.

30:19.937 --> 30:22.689
Yes! OK, are we ready for this? Nachito!

30:22.773 --> 30:25.191
- Bring it on, please. Come on, everybody.
- Bah! Bah!

30:26.109 --> 30:29.780
You won't believe it till you see it
with your own eyes. She's double-jointed.

30:29.863 --> 30:33.408
Blows the candles out on a cupcake
stuck in her own ass.

30:33.491 --> 30:35.744
Yeah, she's a real artist.

30:35.827 --> 30:36.995
Uh... [sighs]

30:37.078 --> 30:39.456
I can't. I got paperwork.

30:39.539 --> 30:42.542
Oh, you're goin'. It's Miller's 40th.

30:42.626 --> 30:44.002
You have to pay your respects.

30:44.085 --> 30:47.672
So, sign the fucking card, pendejo.

30:48.882 --> 30:50.717
Go on and put a twenty in there.

30:53.762 --> 30:56.264
- Holy shit.
- What?

30:57.098 --> 30:59.726
I requested an up-rez
of your photo from last night.

31:00.560 --> 31:03.146
- The kid?
- Yeah, check it out.

31:04.731 --> 31:06.608
Hey, check existing contacts.

31:07.692 --> 31:09.653
Checking.

31:09.736 --> 31:11.529
Boom. Name and last known.

31:11.613 --> 31:13.156
Let's go.

31:14.491 --> 31:16.660
Oh, I thought you had paperwork to do.

31:16.743 --> 31:18.662
No? No? All right.

31:20.622 --> 31:23.333
- Here they are.
- [Nomi] Oh.

31:24.709 --> 31:26.252
- Mm...
- Hey.

31:27.879 --> 31:30.048
Sorry it took so long.
I just wanted to be sure.

31:30.131 --> 31:31.132
There were cops?

31:31.215 --> 31:33.051
There's one staked out front
of your place.

31:33.134 --> 31:35.720
Every couple of hours, an unmarked car
rolls through the alley.

31:36.304 --> 31:37.889
Shit.

31:38.765 --> 31:40.558
Were you able to get hold of Isabella?

31:41.852 --> 31:44.354
She said no problem
using her back entrance.

31:45.522 --> 31:48.232
Thank you guys so much.
I know how much trouble this is.

31:48.316 --> 31:49.985
It's not a problem, Nomi.

31:50.068 --> 31:53.404
After what you did for Lola and me?
You're family.

31:54.238 --> 31:57.534
Clete Tamark. Couple convictions.

31:57.617 --> 31:59.995
Vandalism, disorderly conduct, MIP.

32:00.078 --> 32:03.040
He's running with
the New Maniac Mafia up in Englewood.

32:03.122 --> 32:07.085
What happened to the Old Maniac Mafia?
I miss them.

32:07.878 --> 32:10.171
He's just a kid, too.

32:10.254 --> 32:13.550
They're all kids, Will. They're all kids.

32:24.519 --> 32:26.312
Art is like religion.

32:27.605 --> 32:29.399
For the believers, it's everything.

32:29.482 --> 32:31.026
For anyone else...

32:32.276 --> 32:35.697
it's just a pile of stinking bullshit.

32:50.503 --> 32:51.504
I know you.

33:03.767 --> 33:05.102
Do I know you?

33:06.269 --> 33:08.772
This is not who you are.

33:16.404 --> 33:17.864
Clete! Cops!

33:17.948 --> 33:19.032
Kill him!

33:21.659 --> 33:23.202
[Diego] Oh, shit!

33:25.246 --> 33:27.290
Shit! Fuck!

33:27.373 --> 33:29.459
Hey! Stop!

33:30.376 --> 33:32.336
Boy, you better stop!

33:45.976 --> 33:47.477
I fuckin' hate this shit!

34:10.750 --> 34:11.918
Ah!

34:14.796 --> 34:15.630
[grunts]

34:15.713 --> 34:18.133
- Fuck!
- Get up, get up! Go, go, go!

34:22.137 --> 34:25.223
- [whispers] Kick me. Kick me.
- What?

34:25.306 --> 34:26.683
[whispers] Kick me.

34:50.498 --> 34:52.667
[man] Y'all smell pork?

35:16.024 --> 35:18.401
You in the wrong 'hood, po-po.

35:18.484 --> 35:21.571
- Get yo' bacon-smellin' ass on.
- You motherfuckers on a coffee break?

35:21.654 --> 35:23.240
Yeah, with yo' mama.

35:23.322 --> 35:24.741
[laughter]

35:24.824 --> 35:26.076
[Will] All right.

35:26.743 --> 35:30.080
What's wrong with this nig--?
[laughs] Bye-bye!

35:31.539 --> 35:33.291
OK, we're gonna have some fun.

35:35.459 --> 35:38.379
- [voice echoes] Fucking cut!
- How was it?

35:38.462 --> 35:41.758
I've got a hard-on
that's gonna last all week!

35:41.841 --> 35:45.929
Oh, so natural, so real!

35:46.012 --> 35:48.723
- Bra-vo! Bravo!
- Yes, yes, yes!

35:48.806 --> 35:50.267
- Yes!
- [gun fires]

35:50.349 --> 35:51.350
- I'm sorry.
- Fuck!

35:51.434 --> 35:53.519
I apologize. I'm sorry, man.

35:53.603 --> 35:55.813
- That's in the movie.
- Yeah?

35:55.897 --> 35:57.899
- That's in the movie, Lito!
- It's in the movie?

35:57.982 --> 35:59.358
- Yes! Come on!
- Thank you.

37:22.066 --> 37:24.777
[speaks Korean] Where am I? Where is this?

37:24.861 --> 37:26.237
Nairobi.

37:26.321 --> 37:27.905
[speaks Swahili] Where are you?

37:29.573 --> 37:32.118
- Seoul.
- [chuckles]

37:32.202 --> 37:33.744
[speaks Korean]

37:35.205 --> 37:39.125
- You speak Korean?
- Do you speak Swahili?

37:41.002 --> 37:43.338
Then how are we understanding each other?

37:43.421 --> 37:44.839
I don't know.

37:47.925 --> 37:50.887
You are the spirit of Jean-Claude.

37:50.970 --> 37:54.265
[laughs] I felt your spirit in me.

37:54.349 --> 37:55.892
You are a very good fighter.

37:55.975 --> 37:58.311
You don't know anything about me.

37:58.395 --> 38:02.857
I don't know how,
but I know your name is Sun.

38:04.275 --> 38:08.029
- You have a difficult decision to make.
- Stop. This cannot be real.

38:08.112 --> 38:10.198
What is real is I might have died
if it wasn't for you.

38:10.281 --> 38:11.782
I don't understand this.

38:11.866 --> 38:16.662
So if you do not mind,
I prefer to assume you're a hallucination.

38:17.997 --> 38:19.165
I take no offense.

38:19.249 --> 38:22.960
Since that is resolved,
I would like to continue my walk.

38:23.044 --> 38:24.795
Please.

38:24.879 --> 38:26.923
- Alone.
- Of course.

38:42.397 --> 38:44.107
- You're still here.
- I'm sorry.

38:44.190 --> 38:46.609
I don't know how I came here
or how I go back.

38:46.692 --> 38:50.113
Perhaps there is something in me
that calls or something in you that calls.

38:50.196 --> 38:52.323
I'm not calling you or anyone else.

38:53.116 --> 38:55.034
Perhaps that is the problem.

38:57.536 --> 38:58.788
Are you in trouble?

38:59.872 --> 39:04.210
No. But tomorrow I might be.

39:21.394 --> 39:23.229
I know this choice.

39:24.647 --> 39:27.191
It's like having two different lives.

39:28.526 --> 39:30.361
One will be very dangerous for me.

39:32.155 --> 39:34.407
The other, very bad for my mother.

39:36.575 --> 39:43.166
My question is, am I the person
who wants to see my brother punished,

39:43.249 --> 39:47.837
who wants to watch the business
my father built be destroyed?

39:48.712 --> 39:52.509
Or am I the person
who wants to save them,

39:52.591 --> 39:54.635
who will go to prison for them,

39:54.718 --> 39:59.098
even though they have been cruel to me
for my entire life?

40:00.266 --> 40:02.435
You are afraid.

40:04.895 --> 40:07.565
I feel it for my mother every day.

40:09.775 --> 40:12.153
I promised I would take care of her.

40:13.196 --> 40:15.739
Everything will be all right...

40:16.991 --> 40:18.826
I must keep that promise.

40:20.453 --> 40:22.788
I must keep it, no matter what.

40:24.582 --> 40:28.961
I promised my mother
I would protect my family.

40:29.045 --> 40:33.216
It was the last thing I said to her
before she died.

40:33.299 --> 40:37.011
- If I break it--
- Then your last words become a lie.

40:41.807 --> 40:45.853
Once, when I was eight...

40:47.980 --> 40:50.608
my father's enemies came to our house.

40:51.817 --> 40:54.904
They had big machetes, like this.

40:55.821 --> 40:57.823
My mother had a knife, like this.

40:57.907 --> 41:00.951
They wanted revenge
for what my father's tribe had done.

41:01.035 --> 41:03.246
They wanted me.

41:03.329 --> 41:06.624
My father was gone. She was alone.

41:07.708 --> 41:13.464
But... she put me behind her,
and she faced these men.

41:14.257 --> 41:15.966
They knew they could kill her.

41:16.050 --> 41:19.929
But they also looked her
in the eyes and knew

41:20.012 --> 41:23.474
she would take
at least one of them with her.

41:23.558 --> 41:25.393
And they left.

41:26.603 --> 41:29.188
Because none of them
wanted to be that one.

41:32.858 --> 41:37.863
Who can say if it is
we who make the choice,

41:37.947 --> 41:40.074
or the choice that makes us?

41:45.580 --> 41:47.457
[phone chimes]

42:01.345 --> 42:03.347
[woman 1] ...the ceremony.
The last thing we would...

42:03.431 --> 42:06.183
[woman 2] The color's
really looking nice on her.

42:06.267 --> 42:09.145
- [woman 3] Think it shows the right...
- [woman 2] Where did you have it made?

42:09.228 --> 42:12.565
- The same tailor we normally use?
- I had no idea how heavy it all would be.

42:12.649 --> 42:15.025
[women laughing, chattering]

42:15.776 --> 42:18.279
I hope I don't collapse
in the middle of the circle.

42:18.362 --> 42:20.072
[women chuckling]

42:23.451 --> 42:24.868
Priya!

42:31.041 --> 42:33.794
Priya, I don't want to
pressure anyone, but--

42:33.877 --> 42:36.673
- Sanyam, please!
- All right, all right. Take your time.

42:40.301 --> 42:43.596
[band plays up-tempo music]

43:12.625 --> 43:15.252
[no audible sounds]

44:00.172 --> 44:03.384
[band continues, muted]

45:37.311 --> 45:41.357
I take the first of seven steps with you,
my husband-to-be...

45:43.108 --> 45:48.906
that we may cherish each other
and promise that we will grow together...

45:48.989 --> 45:52.827
in mental and spiritual strength.

45:55.078 --> 45:58.332
[Rajan] I take the fourth
of the seven steps with you...

46:00.167 --> 46:04.797
I take the fifth of seven steps with you,
my husband-to-be,

46:04.881 --> 46:08.300
and promise love and obedience
in all things.

46:19.102 --> 46:22.815
I take the sixth of the seven steps
with you, my wife-to-be...

46:24.066 --> 46:27.027
with the promise of
everlasting companionship.

46:27.110 --> 46:29.906
[no audible dialogue]

46:36.412 --> 46:37.955
We shall share love.

46:38.038 --> 46:40.666
Share the same tastes.

46:53.554 --> 46:55.973
Share the same food.

47:03.272 --> 47:07.735
The final vow, the final step,
is yours, my love.

47:33.761 --> 47:38.307
Let us make a vow together
to share our strengths.

47:41.018 --> 47:42.352
[gasps softly]

47:54.406 --> 47:56.366
We shall be of one mind.

48:07.044 --> 48:09.922
We shall observe these vows together.

48:15.427 --> 48:20.016
Come thou, as I take the last
of seven steps with you and--

48:28.398 --> 48:29.984
What the fuck are you doing?

48:31.610 --> 48:33.403
You're not in love with him.

48:35.572 --> 48:38.701
- Kala? Kala?
- [woman screams]

48:38.784 --> 48:40.410
[audience gasps]
